  <brief_title>Selective Block of the Axillary Nerve in Postoperative Pain Management</brief_title>
  <official_title>Selective Block of the Axillary Nerve in Postoperative Pain Management, a Randomised, Blinded, Placebo-controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
